hopobject.body: I'd like some euros function of endurex If you were watching BBC1 at 05:50 BST this morning you would have seen a newspaper review being presented by Naga Munchetty, who used to present Working Lunch on BBC2, Sally Bundock, who presents World Business Report, and Louise Cooper, who used to present business news on the BBC World Service and is now an independent City commentator. So that's three BBC business presenters chatting about the papers. Excellent.
